Shiho: Look, I have to go now.
Ichika: Shiho...
Ichika: (I didn't manage to talk with her yet again...)
Ichika: (When did I start becoming so awkward around Honami and Shiho? And Saki is...)
Ichika: Is this how it's all going to end? We'll just graduate and split up without ever speaking to each other again?
???: <♪— ♪—>
Ichika: Miku's music video...
Ichika: Miku's amazing... She's always so free and versatile. She can do anything.
Ichika: Unlike me...
Ichika: ...*Sigh*
Ichika: My guitar case is so dusty...
Ichika: (But I guess I won't ever be playing it again...)
Ichika: (We promised each other we'd form a band and be together forever, but now...)
Ichika: Huh?
Ichika: What was that flash of light just now... Did it come from my phone?
Ichika: What's this song? Untitled?
Ichika: Wh-What?! I can't see!
Ichika: Ugh... Where am I?
Ichika: A classroom? But I was literally standing in my room just a moment ago...
Miku: Welcome to your SEKAI!
Ichika: Huh? What? Who?
Ichika: M-Miku?
Miku: That's my name. Nice to meet you, Ichika.
Ichika: This can't be real... And how do you know my name?
Luka: Because this SEKAI is a place that was born from the feelings of you and your friends, Ichika.
Ichika: L-Luka's here too?! I can't even... What's going on?
Luka: Sorry to surprise you like this, but there's nothing to be afraid of. We're here to help you and your friends.
Ichika: Help us...do what?
Luka: We'll help you find your true feelings in this SEKAI.
Miku: Once you do, your feelings will give birth to songs.
Miku: That's why we are here. We want you... no, you and your friends, to find your true feelings again.
Ichika: My friends... You don't mean...
Miku: Don't tell me you've forgotten who your friends are?
Ichika: .....
Little Saki: Playing together, talking about stuff, watching shooting stars on our way home...
Little Saki: I wish we could keep doing all that together forever!
Honami: Oh, no... It's nothing.
Shiho: Look, I have to go now.
Ichika: But...we've all... And Saki, she's...
Miku: It will all be okay, Ichika.
Miku: All of you still feel the same way. I'm sure of it.
Ichika: What?
Miku: So you'll see each other again, right here.
Luka: Miku and I will be waiting for you here too, so come with your friends next time, okay?
Ichika: What are you trying to tell me?
Ichika: Miku! Luka!
Ichika: I...fell asleep? When did I...
Ichika: Feels like I had the strangest dream...
Ichika: I must've been asleep for a while. It's already dark outside.
Ichika: Oh wow.
